<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>YOUR OTP FROM [Trendify]</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1
      style="
        padding: 2rem;
        background-color: rgb(230, 229, 233);
        color: #000000;
      "
    >
      Hi <%= username %>
    </h1>
    <p>
      We've received a request to verify your account on [Trendify]. Your
      One-Time Password (OTP) is:
    </p>
    <h2 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center">
      <%= otp %>
    </h2>
    <p>
      This OTP is valid for only <%= expire %> minutes. Please enter it on the
      verification screen to complete your account setup.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email and contact us
      for assistance.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <p>The [Trendify] Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
